ng in multiple state markets and be accustomed to some of the state by state variability in approaches. As most customers are in higher income brackets, you will be comfortable dealing with sophisticated and well informed buyers and will be nimble enough to adjust your approach in response to marketing campaigns and tactical competitive responses. If you see yourself as a leading Sales Consultant in solar, this is an opportunity to join a business with the best products, great prices and the rewards to support their market ambitions.\n\nPlease click on the ‘Apply Now’ button to submit your confidential application or telephone Andrew Thoseby on (03) 8617 8120 for further information. See ‘Job Search'' on www.facebook.com/1stexecutive where you can apply or register your details.', 'Inside Sales Consultant', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '82-autosave', '', '', '2013-04-05 05:48:35', '2013-04-05 05:48:35', '', 82, 'http://jobboard.1stsocial.com.au/2013/04/05/82-autosave/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
